## Sharing via Hyperlink

### On a network drive

Save the folder to a shared path. The hyperlink is just the file path:

```
file:///S:/Shared/CommandCenter/command-center.html
```

Or on OneDrive/SharePoint, right-click → Copy link.

### On SharePoint/Teams

Upload the HTML file to a SharePoint document library. People can open it in their browser. Note: SharePoint may block some JavaScript — if so, download and open locally.

### As an email attachment

The file is ~1,700 lines, roughly 90KB. You can email it directly. The recipient saves it locally and opens in Chrome/Edge/Firefox.

